    tags: ["Flutter", "C#", "ABP Framework"],
    link: "#",
    linkType: "GitHub"
  },
  {
    icon: "🛍️",
    title: "Kyomu Space",
    description: "Built a custom e-commerce platform for a Colombian women-focused store with full product catalog, user profiles, and shopping cart functionality. Designed an advanced UI/UX and integrated the Nequi payment gateway for secure, seamless transactions. Delivered a complete end-to-end shopping experience from browsing to checkout.",
    tags: ["WordPress", "Nequi API"],
    link: "#",
    linkType: "Visit"
  },
  {
    icon: "💻",
